@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vgkrtm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.46 * tmp + 0.54)))
    v1 = 0.88
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.63)) + (wp.cos(v0 + 0.51) + tmp))
    v0 = 0.34
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
